  ║                                                          ║
  ║  TIERS:                                                  ║
  ║  FREE        5 req total, 10/min, 50/day                ║
  ║  PRO         unlimited, 60/min, 1000/day                ║
  ║  ENTERPRISE  unlimited, 300/min, 10000/day              ║
